review_blob: imo, i havent had a better, commercially available beer.  I found it to be slightly better on tap than out of a bottle, but Im a fan of tap beer so maybe its just me.

this isnt the beer beer on earth, but for 12 bucks for a 36 pack, it cant be beat! along the same line as beast or natty light. Its pretty much the only beer I drink at home. plus its union made so you cant go wrong
